snippet.title: Minecraft x Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles DLC
snippet.description: Cowabunga, dudes and dudettes! The Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles have found their way into Minecraft in this radical DLC. Show off your ninja skills as you take down gnarly enemies like Leatherhead and Krang, explore iconic locations like the Turtle Lair, and save NYC from Shredder – all in the name of pizza, of course! Play as any of the four Turtles, choose from 20 TMNT skins, and make your way through this shell-shocking world! Rep your mutant reptile love with the free Turtle T-Shirt in the Dressing Room. Turtle Power!
